transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra. How can I assist you?

Speaker 2: Yes, hello. I'm calling because I think I was put under an automatic refill and I don't want an automatic refill. I noticed the invoice in my credit card this morning.

Speaker 2: Robert Rodriguez, 122-54.

Speaker 1: Thank you, Robert. Okay, yes, so it does show here that you do have a prescription with us for Viagra AGB, a quantity of 25. So you do receive that every two months,

Speaker 1: No, unfortunately, since this is a prescription, you do have to have a certain monthly interval.

Speaker 2: So if you do not need it every two months, you don't have to have it every two months.

Speaker 1: But like I said, we can always adjust it to every three months or every four months

Speaker 2: or every five months. We can even do every six months.

Speaker 1: Okay, but I don't need the one they're sending me now.

Speaker 2: Okay, well, that one already shipped out, so I'm not able to cancel it

Speaker 1: because it shipped out already. However, I can go ahead and just delay your next shipment.

Speaker 2: We can delay it until June.

Speaker 1: No, let's do six months.

Speaker 2: Okay, you're on six months, and I adjusted it to every six months for you, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay, so when do you have it coming next? What date?

Speaker 2: You're not going to receive another order until the end of July.

Speaker 1: End of July. Okay, thank you.

Speaker 2: Okay, well, you're all set. You're welcome.

Speaker 1: I have another question. I have another question as well.

Speaker 2: My question is when I ordered this, I ordered the new Viagra,

Speaker 1: and what I got was just the Lone Sun.

Speaker 2: So the Lone Sun is still the active ingredient on the AGB.

Speaker 1: The components are much lighter, which is why it starts working faster,

Speaker 2: stays in your system for a longer period of time,

Speaker 1: and why it does not cause any side effects.

Speaker 2: Okay, but I did not receive that.

Speaker 1: I did not receive the Viagra AGB order.

Speaker 2: The Viagra AGB? So on the label, it's just a Greenstone LLC,

Speaker 1: and every pill should also have the number 100 engraved on the pill.

Speaker 2: 100 what?

Speaker 1: It should have the number 100 engraved on the pill.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that's the milligrams,

Speaker 1: but there is a difference between the regular Viagra and the new Viagra, correct?

Speaker 2: Yes, so the regular Classic Viagra should have an engraving that says AC 340,

Speaker 1: and the AGB should have an engraving that says 100.

Speaker 2: Okay, because what I received is not the AC.

Speaker 1: Okay, so what I can go ahead and do for you is that I can ask the pharmacy

Speaker 2: to reship with the correct Viagra AGB.

Speaker 1: Yeah, because I didn't receive that this time, so that's why I ordered.

Speaker 2: Okay, well just to make sure that you do receive the AGB,

Speaker 1: I'll ask the pharmacy to reship the order for you. Okay, Robert?

Speaker 2: Okay, with no extra charge, correct?

Speaker 1: No extra charge, that's correct.

Speaker 2: Thank you so much. I appreciate it.

Speaker 1: You're welcome. Of course. Have a good rest of your day. Bye.

Speaker 2: Okay, bye.
